OL,3,CMural of Bellingham and Rogers eating
OL,4,Corange chips appears in Quinton
OL,6,FA mural of England stars Jude
OL,7,FBellingham and Morgan Rogers eating a
OL,8,Fbag of orange chips has appeared in
OL,9,FQuinton.
OL,11,FThe artwork, which is on the side of
OL,12,FClassic Fryer chip shop on Hagley
OL,13,FRoad, is becoming a real treat for the
OL,14,Feyes of passersby.
OL,16,FBellingham, who is from Stourbridge,
OL,17,Fand Rogers, who is from Halesowen, can
OL,18,Fbe seen tucking into the Black Country
OL,19,Fdelicacy.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/4
