OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F341A1783792086
OL,3,CMural of Bellingham and Rogers eating
OL,4,Corange chips appears in Quinton
OL,6,FOrange chips are a famous staple in
OL,7,Fthe West Midlands. They consist of
OL,8,Fthick-cut chips being coated in batter
OL,9,Fbefore being fried.
OL,11,FBellingham and Rogers are childhood
OL,12,Ffriends and are now playing on the
OL,13,Fbiggest stage in football.
OL,15,FBoth have been preparing for England's
OL,16,FQuarter-final tie against Norway this
OL,17,Fevening (July 11th).
OL,19,FA win in Miami would see the Three
OL,20,FLions only one game away from the
OL,21,FWorld Cup final.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/4
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,342,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F341A1783792086
OL,3,CMural of Bellingham and Rogers eating
OL,4,Corange chips appears in Quinton
OL,6,FSomething the pair would've been
OL,7,Fdreaming of since they were children,
OL,8,Fmaybe while eating some orange chips.
OL,10,FThe mural has been a showstopper, with
OL,11,Fpeople from all from far and wide
OL,12,Fcoming to take a look or a selfie.
OL,14,FThe owner of the chip shop, Ramesh
OL,15,FRatwadia, says the artist has done a
OL,16,Fgreat job, and it is making more
OL,17,Fpeople want to try the Black Country
OL,18,Ftreat.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/4
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
