FL,342,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F341A1783792086
OL,3,CMural of Bellingham and Rogers eating
OL,4,Corange chips appears in Quinton
OL,6,FThe mural also has little details,
OL,7,Fwhich are nods to the players' homes,
OL,8,Fas underneath the England crest on
OL,9,FBellingham's shirt has the name of his
OL,10,Fhometown, Stourbridge, while Rogers'
OL,11,Ffeatures 'Halesowen'.
OL,13,FBoth are accompanied by the flag of
OL,14,Fthe Black Country.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/4
